name: RARE VISITOR! Privilege Style 767-300ER Windy Landing at Calgary Airport
description:
A few weeks ago, this rare 767 from Spanish charter airline Privilege Style paid us a visit, but not on any ordinary charter. This was carrying over 200 refugees from Afghanistan! Welcome to Calgary, and to Canada!
